  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>WELCOME TO CYBERSPACE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">You are a <strong>Cyberdrifter, </strong>part of a team of military tech specialists navigating  cyberspace in VR.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Armed with your <strong>Data Disc, </strong>ride your<strong> cyber cycle</strong> into a<strong> virtualised world and </strong>cleanse the system of a sinister rogue AI.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/607760/extras/dc5f216946f583d8763ebfb2c3b3d9f8.poster.avif?t=1768495022\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/607760/extras/dc5f216946f583d8763ebfb2c3b3d9f8.webm?t=1768495022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/607760/extras/dc5f216946f583d8763ebfb2c3b3d9f8.mp4?t=1768495022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Main Mission</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Ride into cyberspace on your cyber cycle and utilize your data disc to hack or eliminate the virtualised enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/607760/extras/bedece3994f20701fd2c741f211703ff.poster.avif?t=1768495022\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/607760/extras/bedece3994f20701fd2c741f211703ff.webm?t=1768495022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/607760/extras/bedece3994f20701fd2c741f211703ff.mp4?t=1768495022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Cyber Arcade mini-games</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Cyber Drift</strong> - Race your cycle around the neon stadium for leaderboard glory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/607760/extras/a4fda35e9c0adcd62ea9078d5a27e420.poster.avif?t=1768495022\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/607760/extras/a4fda35e9c0adcd62ea9078d5a27e420.webm?t=1768495022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/607760/extras/a4fda35e9c0adcd62ea9078d5a27e420.mp4?t=1768495022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Cyber Blast</strong> - Take down virtual enemies in an arcade-style shooter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <strong>Disc Drift</strong> - Throw your Data Disc at plasma orbs before they reach the danger zone.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Flexible VR comfort</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Support for <strong>seated or standing</strong> play, with smooth locomotion or blink/dash teleport.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Optimized for all major VR controllers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
